Delta 66
</A>
,
<A href="http://www.m-audio.com/images/global/manuals/Delta44_Manual.pdf">
Delta 44
</A>
, Delta 410 and
<A href="http://www.m-audio.com/images/global/manuals/Audiophile2496_Manual.pdf">
Audiophile 2496
</A>
.
